attributes.long-description:
Purchase the Rockstar Games PS Vita Collection to get Midnight Club L.A. Remix, The Warriors, Manhunt 2 and Beaterator on PSP and PS Vita.

Midnight Club L.A. Remix
Race at breakneck speed through the streets of modern day LA in Midnight Club LA Remix.

The Warriors
New York, 1979. A battle on the streets. The armies of the night number 60,000 strong, and tonight they’re all after The Warriors – a street gang wrongly accused of killing a rival gang leader.

Manhunt 2
An experiment at a secret research facility has gone catastrophically wrong. Daniel Lamb and Leo Kasper are the only surviving subjects. The Pickman Project will stop at nothing to hunt them down and stop the truth from getting out.

Beaterator
Rockstar Games© and multi-platinum selling producer Timbaland have designed an incredibly simple to use and portable music making application that allows everyone to create their own music anywhere.

1 - Player
3.7 GB File Size
